data.current_summary: Return list of Flight Offers based on posted searching criteria.
data.summary_suggestion: Search flight offers with complex criteria
data.description_suggestion: Searches for available flight offers using a request body with complex search criteria. Accepts a GetFlightOffersQuery object containing origin, destination, departure date, travelers (with types: ADULT, CHILD, HELD_INFANT, SEATED_INFANT, SENIOR), and travel class preferences. Returns a collection of flight offers with complete itinerary details, pricing breakdown, and baggage allowances. Supports more flexible filtering than the GET endpoint. Results are sourced from multiple airlines and GDS systems. Requires authentication via access token. Test environment uses a subset of production data; use major airports like LON or NYC for reliable results.
